            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "name": "Gulp",
                "ability_type": "Extraordinary",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "A stargazer can open its giant mouth in a fraction of a second, creating a vortex that draws a target into its maw. When underwater, a stargazer gains 5 additional feet of reach with its bite attack and a +2 bonus on combat maneuver checks to grapple. "
            },
