                "ability_type_abbrev": "Ex",
                "text": "Venomous spines\u2014injury; <i>save</i> Fort DC 15; <i>frequency</i> 1/round for 4 rounds; <i>effect</i> sickened for 1d4 rounds; <i>cure</i> 2 consecutive saves. The save DC is Constitution-based. ",
